=head2 OpenRead()

Open a file, whose name is addressed by rax, for read and return the file descriptor in rax


B<Example:>


    Mov rax, Rs($0);                                                              # File to read

    OpenRead;                                                                     # Open file  # 

    PrintOutRegisterInHex rax;
    CloseFile;                                                                    # Close file
